---
title: Creepy Crawly Tagliatelle Pasta with Goblin’s Nose Mushrooms
description: Tagliatelle noodles may wiggle and squirm, but we promise this pasta is no plate of worms. It has a creamy sauce accented with lemon and herby tarragon and is tossed with sliced mushrooms. And because this is Halloween season, we also had to add in a few cloves of garlic (you know, to keep the vampires at bay). All in all, those slithering, al dente strands make for some truly great grub.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/creepy-crawly-tagliatelle-pasta-f052dd29.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/creepy-crawly-tagliatelle-pasta-86d22a62.pdf
servings: 2
